modShortDescription: Allows all gas pumps in game to become shop like. You click on a gas pump you see in the world and you can purchase gas.
modDescription:
Allows all gas pumps in game to become [shop](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-prefab/) like. You click on a gas pump you see in the world and you can purchase gas.

**[Download](https://badpanda.app/HH_Modlets_a20/HH_Gaspumps.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11963-highopes-modlets/).
